PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783521454
OL,3,CHow 300 bathtubs of concrete are
OL,4,Cending up in Thames Water sewers every
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,F"We are urging construction companies
OL,8,Fto be more vigilant in their disposal
OL,9,Fof concrete, to prevent damage to our
OL,10,Fsewer network, as it takes valuable
OL,11,Ftime and resource away from essential
OL,12,Finfrastructure upgrade," said Tim
OL,13,FDavies, Head of Waste for North London.
OL,15,F"The concrete removal process can be
OL,16,Fextremely complex. In many cases, we
OL,17,Fuse high-pressure cutting units to
OL,18,Fbreak down concrete within the sewer
OL,19,Fbefore it can be safely removed.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1783521454
OL,3,CHow 300 bathtubs of concrete are
OL,4,Cending up in Thames Water sewers every
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,F"This work requires significant
OL,8,Finvestment with expensive equipment, a
OL,9,Flarge team of skilled engineers, and a
OL,10,Fconsiderable amount of time to
OL,11,Fcomplete.
OL,13,F"Our teams are working closely with
OL,14,Fconstruction companies across our
OL,15,Fcommunities to raise awareness of the
OL,16,Fserious damage and disruption caused
OL,17,Fby improper disposal.
OL,19,F"My message to businesses and
OL,20,Fcontractors is simple: please ensure
OL,21,Fconcrete is disposed of correctly.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/4
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
