OL,3,CHow 300 bathtubs of concrete are
OL,4,Cending up in Thames Water sewers every
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FPreventing this issue in the first
OL,8,Fplace is far more effective than
OL,9,Fdealing with the consequences later,"
OL,10,Fhe explained.
